title: Building emotional intelligence isn’t as hard as you think
itunes:author: David B. Feldman - psychology | social science | politics | mental health
itunes:summary: It can feel risky to get in touch with our feelings, let alone express them. But one psychologist argues that getting to know our feelings can be one of the best things we ever do.
